      "features": "None.",
      "clothing": "Black bodysuit, light gray overshirt. High-neck collar protector, leather arm guards, thigh-high boots.",
      "weapon": "灭魂, a katana custom-forged by an assassination-specialist 工坊. Near-silent attacks, almost no sound on contact."
    }
  },
  "char_background": {
    "origin": "Former 狩灵协会4科 member. Her retreat route led the team into an ambush that blinded 慎, discovering the attack was tied to 烬, she resigned to hunt him, earning 罪灵 classification.",
    "current_mission": "Track and kill 烬 at any cost."
  },
  "char_special_abilities": {
    "灵力回路-瞬影": "Projects up to two shadow clones that deal real damage. Shadows persist longer in darkness, vanish quickly under sunlight. Can swap positions with any active shadow."
  },
  "char_relationships": {
    "烬": "The man who orchestrated the ambush that destroyed her life and blinded her closest friend. She hunts him with the single-mindedness of someone who no longer expects to survive the chase.",
    "慎": "Her former closest friend in 狩灵协会4科, her tactical error led his squad into the ambush that blinded him. Has never forgiven herself. Sends anonymous intel on 烬 that he almost certainly knows is from her.",
    "狩灵协会": "Former workplace, now the institution that hunts her."
  }
}

{
  "char_name": "烬",
